resourceInfo.abstract:
FY2014
Building upon the springs and seeps inventory previously funded by the Desert LCC, this project creates a publicly available geospatial database of approximately 2,000+ known Great Basin springs. Create a summary report on the biotic and abiotic conditions of the known springs.
